00:06:06.784 --> 00:06:09.076
and it might not be 100% effective.

00:06:09.076 --> 00:06:13.101
So really, ideally, you've just got to use it on an area that doesn't have hair

00:06:13.101 --> 00:06:17.174
and if it does have hair, just very gently try to pull it off or resort to using isoproply myristate, which you can get

00:06:17.315 --> 00:06:19.475
at cosmetic- oh, makeup stores.

